Description
------------------------------------------------

This is a simple bash script that looks for patterns in the files through grep and uses awk to filter out the required details.
List of files explored:
1. /etc/hosts
2. /etc/ssh/ssh_config
3. ~/.ssh/ssh_config
4. ~/.ssh/known_hosts
5. ~/.ssh/authorized_keys

Execution
-----------------------------------------------
To execute the program, just run ./discovery


